premise_source_doc_sentence: Leonid Ilyich Brezhnev  (  ˈ ; Леоні́д Іллі́ч Бре́жнєв , 19 December 1906  (  O.S. 6 December  )  -- 10 November 1982  )  was the General Secretary of the Central Committee  (  CC  )  of the Communist Party of the Soviet Union  (  CPSU  )  , presiding over the country from 1964 until his death in 1982 .
Brezhnev was born in Kamenskoye  (  Dneprodzerzhinsk , now Kamianske , Ukraine  )  into a Russian worker 's family in 1906 .
Leonid Brezhnev  (  1906 -- 1982  )  , political leader of the USSR from 1964 to 1982
The name was applied from 1982 to 1988 , in honor of Leonid Brezhnev , to the city of Naberezhnye Chelny in Tatarstan .
Leonid Brezhnev was the leader of the CPSU from 1964 until his death in 1982 , whose eighteen-year reign was recognised as the time of social and economic stagnation in the late Soviet Union .
